Sentencas: The flower-shaped ZnO was synthesized to form composite with the delafossite structure CuFeO2.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composite heterojunction formed for the ZnO-CuFeO2 composite material demonstrates a profound significance for exploring novel materials in solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) field.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 550 degrees C, power outputs of 300 mW cm(-2) and 468 mW cm(-2) were achieved for SOFC devices using pure ZnO and composite with CuFeO2 as the electrolytes, respectively.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composite showed a good performance at low temperatures, for instance, it showed a power output of 148 mW cm(-2) at 430 degrees C.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The studies on photocurrent-time curves with visible light on/off irradiation provided an evidence for electron-hole separation.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The heterojunctions separate holes and electrons, preventing short-circuiting while used in the SOFC device.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These results demonstrate that introducing the heterojunctions in the electrolyte is an innovative approach for advanced SOFCs.
Titulo: The heterogeneous electrolyte of CuFeO2 nano-flakes composited with flower-shaped ZnO for advanced solid oxide fuel cells
